{"id":"api/core/ViewEncapsulation","title":"ViewEncapsulation","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/ViewEncapsulation\", \"name\": \"ViewEncapsulation\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewencapsulation\">ViewEncapsulation<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#viewencapsulation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label enum\">enum</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8k57rh7h6tm47h6y6mag9ndsb\">定义可用于 Component 的 <a href=\"api/core/Component\"><code>Component</code></a> 的模板和样式封装选项。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"enum-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nenum <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\"><span class=\"member-name\">Emulated</span>: 0</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\"><span class=\"member-name\">None</span>: 2</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\"><span class=\"member-name\">ShadowDom</span>: 3</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4jtyh0a1k4j9whxf6sphee3pn\">查看\n<a href=\"api/core/Component#encapsulation\"><code>Component#encapsulation</code></a>。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1a2w3yw1sfd3c9fwawva651eu\">进一步的信息可在\n<a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a>中找到。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"members\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"members\">成员列表<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#members\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>成员</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"Emulated\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">Emulated</span>: 0</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7wrdbykzsf9ibn1ckku475bo0\">通过向组件的宿主元素添加特定属性，并将相同属性应用于通过\n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\"><code>Component#styles</code></a>或\n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\"><code>Component#styleUrls</code></a>提供的所有 CSS 选择器，模拟原生 Shadow DOM 封装行为。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dly6uuk3bwpezgco0668ume4u\">这是默认选项。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"None\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">None</span>: 2</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dhtbki8n2craalgxpi3uso79q\">不提供任何形式的 CSS 样式封装，这意味着通过\n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\"><code>Component#styles</code></a>或\n<a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\"><code>Component#styleUrls</code></a>提供的所有样式都适用于应用程序中任何 HTML 元素，而不考虑它们的宿主组件。</p>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ShadowDom\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">ShadowDom</span>: 3</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cte63c1k03az0ffm3hohf7ylm\">使用浏览器的原生 Shadow DOM API 来封装 CSS 样式，这意味着它会为组件的宿主元素创建一个\nShadowRoot，然后用该元素来封装所有组件的样式。</p>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"example\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"lzz2v4ucg07faxnpe2bu1wa1\">范例<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example path=\"core/ts/metadata/encapsulation.ts\" region=\"longform\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app-root',\n  template: `\n    &lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\n    &lt;span class=\"red\"&gt;Shadow DOM Rocks!&lt;/span&gt;\n  `,\n  styles: [\n    `\n      :host {\n        display: block;\n        border: 1px solid black;\n      }\n      h1 {\n        color: blue;\n      }\n      .red {\n        background-color: red;\n      }\n    `,\n  ],\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>,\n})\nclass MyApp {}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ID\n - api/core/CompilerOptions\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Renderer2\n - api/core/RendererType2\n - errors/NG2009\n - guide/complex-animation-sequences\n - guide/view-encapsulation\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#encapsulation\n - api/core/Component#styleUrls\n - api/core/Component#styles\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#example\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#members\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#viewencapsulation\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts\n-->"}